'''''The Golden Path''''' is a [[point-and-click adventure]] [[video game]] published in 1986 by [[Telecomsoft#Firebird|Firebird Software]]. The game's [[player character]] is Y'n Hsi, a Chinese [[Bhikkhu]] (Buddhist monk) and nobleman. Y'n Hsi seeks to depose Ch'un Kuei, a tyrannical [[warlord]] who murdered Y'n Hsi's father.<ref>{{Cite web |title=The Golden Path (1986) |url=https://www.mobygames.com/game/golden-path |access-date=2022-06-10 |website=MobyGames}}</ref>

